    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-02-13T19:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-02-13T19:00:00-05:00" n="944"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d944">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.1163/1041: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-02-13T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 13, 1941—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>106. Peiping’s no. 529, December 29 [<hi rend="italic">21</hi>], 1 p.m. and
                    despatch 2995, December 30, 1940,<note n="23" xml:id="d944fn1">Neither
                        printed.</note> in regard to the withdrawal of American missionaries from
                    Shansi Province because of the persecution of Chinese adherents.</p>
                <p>It is assumed that you are keeping this matter in mind with a view to taking an
                    appropriate occasion, in your discretion, of bringing it to the attention of the
                    Japanese Foreign Minister<note n="24" xml:id="d944fn2">Yosuke Matsuoka.</note>
                    as another example of apparently deliberate action on the part of the Japanese
                    military in China to interfere with American citizens and their normal
                    legitimate activities, and that you will in due course report to the Department
                    such conversation as you may have with the Foreign Minister on this subject.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
